<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (yswʿ mlk ạlmlwk yswʿ rb ạlạ̉rbạb)2
 (ḥnạn wrḥym wṭwyl ạlrwḥ)2
 1- btrtẖy llḍʿyf ạlly ạlsẖr wqʿh wṣrạkẖ ạlmskyn ạ̹nt btsmʿh
 wạlly ytʿlq byk bạ̹ydk btnjyh ḥty̱ f ywm ạlḍyq btyjy wtrfʿh
 2- btlms ạlḥzyn ạlly qlbh bywjʿh wtnạdy ʿ ạlly tạh wbḥb trjʿh
 wʿynyk mftwḥyn ʿ ạlly tʿbạn snyn trsl lyh slạm lrwḥh ysẖjʿh
 3- yạ bkẖt ạlly qlbh bnwrk ạhtdy̱ wạlly btskn fyh bykwn ʿmrh ạbtdạ
 mʿ ạ̹n ạlqlwb bttḥwl bʿyd tftḥ ạ̹ydk tsẖbʿ kl ḥy rḍy̱</lyrics>
<title>yswʿ mlk ạlmlwk yswʿ rb ạlạ̉rbạb</title>
